1 Niṣpannam āsīt tasya vākyam
2 Guruḥ paramaḥ, tataś ca sapekṣayā
3 Mama darśane paśyati sma yadi santuṣṭaḥ aham āsam;

22 Bhavatīnāṃ śaṅkātmikā svabhāvaḥ satyatām pratipadyamānā
23 abhilāṣaṃ nirmimīte, antaśca tava tāṃ vyācakṣate,
24 yathā cittaṃ tatas tasyāṃ niyojayati;

34 Adyaiva tvayi prakāśate yāvatī
35 satyasyāvasthā janānāṃ yathārthadarśinām
36 yeṣāṃ prītiḥ svayam eva stutyā vastuṣu;

40 "Tava vacanaṃ mama ca anuvartamānaṃ medhā",
41 aham enam prati avocat, "premaṃ prakāśitam cakāra,
42 api tu etad mama samsayam eva adhikam cakāra;

67 Ye yuktiyuktena antaṃ prāpuḥ,
68 te 'sya svābhāvikyā svātantryasya pratyabudhyanta;
69 atas te loke naitikatvam atyajanta.

76 Candramāḥ, prāyaḥ madhyarātrau tarde,
77 akārṣīt tārāḥ asmābhiḥ dṛśyamānāḥ viśīrṇāḥ,
78 bhūtvā yathā ekaḥ śuṣkaḥ kaṣṭhaḥ yaḥ sadā dahyati;

82 Tathā ca sā dayāluḥ chāyā yasya nimittam
83 Pietola adhikaṃ prasiddhaḥ asti Mantua-nagarāt,
84 mama bhāraṃ nyastavān;

97 Tatas tasmāt ūrdhvaṃ śīghram āgacchan
98 sarvā sā mahān nikāyaḥ calati sma;
99 dvau ca agre rudantau āhatur:

100 "Marīyā parvatam prati dhavati sma;
101 caesaras tu ilerdām abhibhavituṃ
102 marsiliyāṃ prāpya tato hiṣpāniyāṃ jagāma."

109 ayam yaḥ jīvati, na ca khalu aham yūyaṃ mṛṣāmi,
110 icchati upari gantum, yāvat sūryaḥ asmān prakāśayati;
111 atas naḥ bruta kutaḥ santike vidvaraḥ."

112 Etāni vacāṃsi āsīt mama duṣaḥ;
113 Ekaśca teṣām ātmānām āha: "Āgaccha
114 Paścād asmākam, tatra tvam prāpsyase vivaram."

121 Evaṃ caikasya pādo mṛtyuloke sthitaḥ,
122 yaḥ śīghram eva tadvanaṃ royiṣyati,
123 duḥkhitaśca bhaviṣyati śaktimavānabhavata iti;

127 Na jānāmi kim punar abravīt sa vā tathāiva tuṣṭāva,
128 tiryag hi tathāvidham asmābhiḥ atiśīghram atiśrītam āsīt;
129 etad eva tu śrutam mayā, tat ca dhārayitum mama priyam abhavat.

142 yasya anye api jāyante vividhāḥ;
143 evam caikasmin anyasmin viṣaye viṣayāntare ca vicintayam,
144 yena cakṣuṣī me nidrāvasāt prāvṛte.
